  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/3b3f3731cea1a9f606b3fb6fc80795d0.avif?t=1768314866\" width=500 height=828 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moduwar</strong> is a <strong>Real-Time Strategy</strong> game that redefines the genre with its unique modular gameplay. Instead of commanding traditional units, you control the <strong>Modu</strong>, a highly adaptable native species of water-dwelling creature capable of <strong>growing, merging, and splitting their organic structures in real time</strong>. By strategically evolving different organs, you create custom units that adapt to any battle scenario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/9c18bea88bee920b99208bd570ee80ef.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/9c18bea88bee920b99208bd570ee80ef.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/9c18bea88bee920b99208bd570ee80ef.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use resources to grow your Modu starting with the heart, the most vital organ you must protect at all costs. You can expand your Modu by growing tiles off your body and placing new organs on top of them. As you play, you learn to grow more useful and specialized organs to face any battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/86ed9d6c1f6557390c9816bf70646401.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/86ed9d6c1f6557390c9816bf70646401.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/86ed9d6c1f6557390c9816bf70646401.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Split tiles into singular organ units to scout your enemies quickly and give yourself the strategic advantage. Split and merge multiple tiles to build your armada, combine your organs to unlock unique abilities, send them to war or merge back with your main body to stand your ground!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/8d8f3bfd9d51abe525ab6999955d83b0.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/8d8f3bfd9d51abe525ab6999955d83b0.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/8d8f3bfd9d51abe525ab6999955d83b0.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>In the single-player campaign, you fight for survival and liberation, unlocking new organ combinations and evolving abilities while commanding one of three distinct factions, but the battle doesn’t end there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/036e8dd7506f901524d97cebbeb27c3e.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/036e8dd7506f901524d97cebbeb27c3e.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/036e8dd7506f901524d97cebbeb27c3e.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Moduwar offers multiple game modes in addition to the single-player campaign:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer (Up to 4 Players) – Compete or cooperate in dynamic battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arena Mode – Test your best Modu builds in intense battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival Mode – Face relentless waves of enemies in a fight for endurance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Skirmish – Engage in tactical battles with customizable settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/6c5ec299021c845b637887d67ee42626.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in the rich and dangerous world of Arkadia, Moduwar immerses you in an alien ecosystem filled with awe-inspiring and terrifying creatures. However, Arkadia is under siege—two invading forces, the technologically advanced Humans and the ruthless Chimera, have enslaved the native Modu, turning them into living weapons of war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Modu forced to serve the ERE - Earth Repatriation Expedition. Will you continue to fight under the ERE, or break the shackles and set yourself free?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will determine the fate of all life on Arkadia, the galaxy and the Moduwar! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moduwar</strong> is a <strong>Real-Time Strategy</strong> game that redefines the genre with its unique modular gameplay. Instead of commanding traditional units, you control the <strong>Modu</strong>, a highly adaptable native species of water-dwelling creature capable of <strong>growing, merging, and splitting their organic structures in real time</strong>. By strategically evolving different organs, you create custom units that adapt to any battle scenario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/9c18bea88bee920b99208bd570ee80ef.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/9c18bea88bee920b99208bd570ee80ef.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/9c18bea88bee920b99208bd570ee80ef.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use resources to grow your Modu starting with the heart, the most vital organ you must protect at all costs. You can expand your Modu by growing tiles off your body and placing new organs on top of them. As you play, you learn to grow more useful and specialized organs to face any battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/86ed9d6c1f6557390c9816bf70646401.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/86ed9d6c1f6557390c9816bf70646401.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/86ed9d6c1f6557390c9816bf70646401.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Split tiles into singular organ units to scout your enemies quickly and give yourself the strategic advantage. Split and merge multiple tiles to build your armada, combine your organs to unlock unique abilities, send them to war or merge back with your main body to stand your ground!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/8d8f3bfd9d51abe525ab6999955d83b0.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/8d8f3bfd9d51abe525ab6999955d83b0.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/8d8f3bfd9d51abe525ab6999955d83b0.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>In the single-player campaign, you fight for survival and liberation, unlocking new organ combinations and evolving abilities while commanding one of three distinct factions, but the battle doesn’t end there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/036e8dd7506f901524d97cebbeb27c3e.poster.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/036e8dd7506f901524d97cebbeb27c3e.webm?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/036e8dd7506f901524d97cebbeb27c3e.mp4?t=1768314866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Moduwar offers multiple game modes in addition to the single-player campaign:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer (Up to 4 Players) – Compete or cooperate in dynamic battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arena Mode – Test your best Modu builds in intense battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival Mode – Face relentless waves of enemies in a fight for endurance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Skirmish – Engage in tactical battles with customizable settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/923100/extras/6c5ec299021c845b637887d67ee42626.avif?t=1768314866\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in the rich and dangerous world of Arkadia, Moduwar immerses you in an alien ecosystem filled with awe-inspiring and terrifying creatures. However, Arkadia is under siege—two invading forces, the technologically advanced Humans and the ruthless Chimera, have enslaved the native Modu, turning them into living weapons of war.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Modu forced to serve the ERE - Earth Repatriation Expedition. Will you continue to fight under the ERE, or break the shackles and set yourself free?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will determine the fate of all life on Arkadia, the galaxy and the Moduwar! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
